<span id="freeTextContainer12091072948503192161">SPOILER ALERT!!!!<br/>I agree with the reviewers who felt confused by this book. Pic out seems to be moving in a new direction with her last two books; wolves and now elephants. This latest novel of hers was all over the place in characters, setting, and plot. By the end, I felt like she was imitating film directer M. Night Shyamalan---&quot;I see dead people&quot;. </span>
